{"id": "1198150505646542858", "channel_id": "1197600495599100086", "type": 0, "author_id": "456226577798135808", "author_name": "Deleted User", "author_bot": false, "content": "<:462646481535631360:684391683680501774>", "timestamp": "2024-01-20T06:22:21.106000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197600495599100086", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.1下篇「深海界域」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1198156281618366525", "channel_id": "1197600495599100086", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "一码归一码。这里是两码事：1. 混沌能叠触手肯定是反设定的，官方也确认放弃了。2. 就目前深海的强度来说，弱，也和自身叠触手数量困难有联系。如果能够促进触手数量的叠加，对全系和各个流派的加强肯定都是有帮助的。这一思路的具体方案还不明确。", "timestamp": "2024-01-20T06:45:18.205000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197600495599100086", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.1下篇「深海界域」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1198156853654323240", "channel_id": "1197600495599100086", "type": 0, "author_id": "632653171642335272", "author_name": "walker747", "author_bot": false, "content": "至于从昨天提到今天的《撕卡》，我还是没能完全理解其意思。我个人觉得，只要是深海系的角色，会叠个触手数量都是合情合理的，整体强度要整体看待，包括费用、附加项数值，联动等。", "timestamp": "2024-01-20T06:47:34.589000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1197600495599100086", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.1下篇「深海界域」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
